      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, and the double VANOS system operates with surgical precision. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory damping rates, and the chassis remains stiff and communicative. Presented in showroom condition with documented service history, it is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
